{\"ngram\": \"waters\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was chosen for its legendary Teahupo'o wave, which Vaast, also 22, first surfed when he was eight years old.\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its legendary Teahupo'o wave\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He made a fine start to the final with a near-perfect 9.5 ride, before Australia's Jack Robinson replied with a 7.83.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 590, \"end\": 599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9450448634249401, \"rank\": 0.03411865776971618, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9811825197748337, \"rank\": 0.012159944012778796, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fine start\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"a near-perfect 9.5 ride\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vaast's next wave gave him a total of 17.67 and Robinson was unable to register another ride as Vaast became the first Olympic champion from Tahiti.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 638, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http:/