\": \"three waves\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"the ocean\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He felt there was a spiritual energy, specific to the region, driving him to the gold medal.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a spiritual energy\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"the region\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have a good relationship [with the surf].\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good relationship\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"the surf\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We call it the 'mana', and in this contest I felt it the whole time,\\\" Vaast said.\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 'mana\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"this contest\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am proud to say that surfing was born in Polynesia, and this means a lot for me.\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9805146131521615, \"rank\": 0.019872612387633198, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"surfing\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dream came true.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The dream\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope this will be a source of inspiration to the youth of Tahiti.\\\"\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1280, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9997581430416503, \"rank\": 0.0002418834774558242, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a source\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"inspiration\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"the youth\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vaast had beaten Peru's Alonso Correa in the semi-finals, while Robinson overcame Brazil's Gabriel Medina.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1290, \"end\": 1295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}, {\"begin\": 1307, \"end\": 1311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998885732628, \"rank\": 1.1142657210228087e-07, \"text\": \"Peru\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Correa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.604090869573561e-16, \"text\": \"Correa\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Correa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Correa\"}, {\"begin\": 1354, \"end\": 1362, \"title